Project: FFPredict — Dynasty Fantasy Football Value Predictor
Owner: Dynasty player who values long-term player value over weekly points

CONTEXT:
- I play dynasty leagues (keep players forever, not redraft)
- I care about: age curves, positional scarcity, rookie value, trade ROI
- My Sleeper username is: REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_SLEEPER_USERNAME
- Data sources: Sleeper public API (free, no key) plus FantasyCalc + KeepTradeCut for market clears

RULES:
- Explain every change in plain English; assume I am not a full-time developer
- Keep Python readable; short comments where the math or API is non-obvious
- When adding features, prefer ONE focused change per step
- Before altering working behavior, describe the preview or plan in the chat first
- Dynasty scoring priority in our custom layer: Age > Usage trend > Team situation > Draft capital

STACK (this repo):
- Streamlit UI in app.py
- Core logic in fantasy_trade_analyzer.py and valuation_engine.py
- Custom 0–100 rules layer in dynasty_custom_score.py
- Sleeper + FantasyCalc + KTC fetches with disk cache under .fantasy_cache (and local JSON history files); not browser localStorage
